title: Hobby Connect
about: Hobby Connect is a web-based platform where people in your local area/city can to, and create an event on a certain date and time on a calendar for other users to see.
languages: Node.js, Express, Sequelize, Handlebars, MySQl, JavaScript

title: Google Book Search
about: Google Book Search is a MERN stack application, That allows you to search and save books from google.

title: V-Bloggers
about: V-Bloggers is an application that allows you to search for youtube content producers in your local area using Goggle Maps lat and long. This project was a colaborated with 3 other people.

title: Weather Dashboard
about: The Weather Dashboard is a great application that shows you Weather Forecasts for 5 days, it also stores previous searches for quick access. This application is perfect for people that love to travel.

title: Code Quizz
about: The code quizz is a mulitable choice based quizz. The quizz has 5 questions that you have to complete within the required time. If you bet the time and finish all the questions you will add you name to the highest scorer page.

title: Employee Directory
about: The Employee Directory is a great tool for a manager or supervisor to have their employees important information all on one page. It also allows each column to be sort in alphabetical order 9

title: Budget Tracker
about: Budget Tracker is a simple app that allows you to track your income and spending, it also puts all your inputs into a graph for easier visualization

title: Employee Tracker
about: Employee Tracker is a node.js application that keeps track of your employees, there role in the company and who there manager is.

title: Burger
about: Burger is an application where you can add burgers you want to try to a list and then once you have tried the burger you can devour it.

title: Fitness Tracker
about: The Fitness Tracker is a web-based application that you can use to record your daily workout.
